    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01262.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">431 Stevens Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1882-01-18">Jan: 18 '82</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My dear Mrs Childs<ptr target="loc.01262_n1"/></salute>
            </opener>

            <p>Yours &#38; Mr Childs', inviting me to dine &#38; meet Mr Wilde received &#38;
                appreciated&#8212;But I am an invalid&#8212;just suffering an extra bad spell &#38;
                forbidden to go out nights this weather&#8212;</p>
            <p>Please give my hearty salutation &#38;
                American welcome to Mr Wilde&#8212;</p>
            <p>I much desire my friend to briefly report &#38; give my respects in person to you
                &#38; shall try to do so soon&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01262.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
